WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:16.823 --> 00:00:19.304
Honey! Where are you? 

00:00:22.928 --> 00:00:25.355
I got new shoes for you.

00:00:25.355 --> 00:00:26.787
Your feet won’t hurt now

00:00:26.787 --> 00:00:29.283
when you go out to distribute gifts.

00:00:29.283 --> 00:00:32.444
I won’t be needing them anymore.

00:00:34.813 --> 00:00:38.164
Oh God! What is this!?

00:00:38.164 --> 00:00:40.568
Santa has lost his job!!!

00:00:40.568 --> 00:00:43.907
They must have surely outsourced his job to China.

00:00:43.917 --> 00:00:46.106
May bad things happen to these Chinese..

00:00:46.106 --> 00:00:48.169
What will happen to us?

00:00:55.196 --> 00:00:58.587
Oh Tirupati Balaji,
I will make Santa shave his head...

00:00:58.587 --> 00:01:01.667
hmmmmm...

00:01:01.667 --> 00:01:03.007
....no....

00:01:03.007 --> 00:01:07.604
okay…I will offer 5% …no..no…10% of his salary

00:01:07.604 --> 00:01:10.608
you just get back Santa's job - Balaji.

00:01:17.008 --> 00:01:21.711
Stop all that crying, I haven't lost my job.

00:01:21.711 --> 00:01:24.871
On the contrary, I am going to deliver millions of gifts this year

00:01:24.871 --> 00:01:26.961
Ho, ho, ho!

00:01:27.659 --> 00:01:30.587
Is that so!? Thank God!!

00:01:31.951 --> 00:01:34.223
Did you just say millions of gifts?

00:01:34.223 --> 00:01:36.914
Have you gone mad? At your age

00:01:36.914 --> 00:01:39.395
how are going to deliver so many gifts?

00:01:39.395 --> 00:01:41.459
You think you are Rajanikanth(the Indian movie star) or what?

00:01:41.459 --> 00:01:46.083
Or you think Vijay Mallya is my chacha
to send you his not-in-use aeroplanes?

00:01:46.083 --> 00:01:50.008
Now now……why are you needlessly
increasing your blood pressure.

00:01:50.008 --> 00:01:52.483
Facebook is there, simple,

00:01:52.483 --> 00:01:54.039
I will deliver through facebook.

00:01:54.039 --> 00:01:55.678
Facebook?

00:01:55.678 --> 00:01:57.498
That Mrs Ambani was saying,

00:01:57.498 --> 00:02:00.816
that facebook will come out with a public issue soon.

00:02:00.816 --> 00:02:03.219
If it lists on Bombay Stock Exchange...,

00:02:03.219 --> 00:02:06.563
then I am surely going to buy 100 shares.

00:02:10.004 --> 00:02:13.407
By the way, you havn't told me - what is the gift?

00:02:13.407 --> 00:02:17.064
FREE online subscription to learn a foreign language…

00:02:17.064 --> 00:02:22.055
You mean French, German, Spanish, Japanese, Chinese ?

00:02:24.404 --> 00:02:26.494
Yes my dear, but what happened to you?

00:02:26.494 --> 00:02:30.082
You understand how important it is
to learn a foreign language nowadays?

00:02:30.082 --> 00:02:31.797
Don’t you underestimate me!

00:02:31.797 --> 00:02:35.995
Even our maid knows how important it is - but online?

00:02:35.995 --> 00:02:38.275
Yes my dear, why not?

00:02:38.275 --> 00:02:40.006
Education also has to move with the times

00:02:40.006 --> 00:02:43.186
And then this is not any silly website,

00:02:43.186 --> 00:02:45.199
they are changing the way people all over the world

00:02:45.199 --> 00:02:49.096
study a language by combining
education with entertainment. 

00:02:49.096 --> 00:02:50.122
Is that so !?

00:02:50.122 --> 00:02:53.165
Yes!!!  Funny animation videos,

00:02:53.165 --> 00:02:55.003
very simple explanations,

00:02:55.003 --> 00:02:57.737
fun exercises and so much more

00:02:57.737 --> 00:02:59.487
education...,

00:02:59.487 --> 00:03:01.472
and along with it - entertainment.

00:03:01.472 --> 00:03:06.305
So you will post it on a million walls
all by yourself?

00:03:06.305 --> 00:03:09.107
No my dear, I will post it on some walls

00:03:09.107 --> 00:03:12.339
and they in turn will post it
on the walls of their friends.

00:03:12.339 --> 00:03:14.742
And why would people do that?

00:03:14.742 --> 00:03:16.205
Hmm…because...

00:03:16.205 --> 00:03:19.034
because...it is a great gift and it is FREE !!

00:03:19.034 --> 00:03:21.343
No, I have a better idea. Listen,

00:03:21.343 --> 00:03:22.262
if you tell people,

00:03:22.262 --> 00:03:25.792
that if they post it to the
facebook wall of 20 other people,

00:03:25.792 --> 00:03:29.214
then within 24 hours
something good will happen to them,

00:03:29.214 --> 00:03:34.282
then you will see...it will become more popular
than even that "Kolaveri"

00:03:34.582 --> 00:03:37.006
Come on! Such a cheap idea.

00:03:37.006 --> 00:03:39.036
I can’t do this,

00:03:39.036 --> 00:03:41.544
after all, I too have some reputation? 

00:03:41.544 --> 00:03:44.783
I bring people 100% genuine gifts, 

00:03:44.783 --> 00:03:45.959
no deals business!

00:03:45.959 --> 00:03:48.907
You just watch, I will post it on people's walls

00:03:48.907 --> 00:03:50.948
and they will happily accept this gift

00:03:50.948 --> 00:03:52.724
and even share it with their friends.

